/**
 * seedPharmacyRestock.js  (R7gz)
 *
 * Comprehensive restock layered on top of seedPharmacy.js. Adds ~220
 * commonly-used Indian formulary drugs across every therapeutic class
 * the original seed missed (antivirals, antifungals, anaesthesia,
 * hematology, emergency-trolley, expanded antibiotics / cardiac /
 * gastro / neuro / respiratory, modern antidiabetics, etc).
 *
 * Idempotent — skips drugs that already exist by `name`. Adds 1–2
 * fresh batches per newly-created drug so FEFO / dispense / indent
 * flows have something to chew on immediately. Also cleans the four
 * pre-existing test rows ("probe", "Test Paracetamol 500mg",
 * "Audit Test Drug", "RT-Test Diclofenac 50mg") if --clean-test
 * is passed.
 *
 * Run:
 *   node Backend/scripts/seedPharmacyRestock.js
 *   node Backend/scripts/seedPharmacyRestock.js --clean-test
 *   node Backend/scripts/seedPharmacyRestock.js --batches-only   (skip drug create)
 */
